column1: Collision indicies for all agents. Each row represnets an agent's collision indicies. Every num_agents rows correspond to an iteration. The latter are synchronized with the timestamp. The format becomes: row1: colIdx(agent1 @ t=1), row2: colIdx(agent2 @ t=1), ... row_num_agents: colIdx(agent_num_agents @ t=1), row_(num_agents+1): colIdx(agent1 @ t=2), row_(num_agents+1): colIdx(agent2 @ t=2), ... row_(2*num_agents): colIdx(agent_num_agents @ t=1) ...
